10 ounce Chicken Strips
2.75 ounce Corn
3.5 ounce Spiced Vegetable Broth
1 ounce Sharp Cheddar Cheese
2 ounce Sour Cream
1 teaspoon Cholula Sauce
1.5 teaspoon Chili, Cumin & Paprika Blend
1 unit Chicken Stock Concentrate
6 unit Flour Tortillas
13.25 ounce Cannellini Beans
1 tablespoon Butter
Cooking Oil
Salt
Pepper

Please refer to the recipe card for Step 1.